    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable example of the E46 chassis, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with factory-spec individual throttle bodies. This unit boasts a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a fully serviced variable M differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced for structural longevity. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings, ensuring the tactile feedback and neutral handling characteristic of this platform. This is a collector-grade vehicle with zero deferred maintenance, presenting in showroom condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
