    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence, maintained to a standard that rivals a showroom floor. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish with a professional ceramic coating that provides a mirror-like reflection and total protection; you will find no stone chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched luxury. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from any creases or wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been garaged in a climate-controlled environment and serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule at authorized centers. All service records are organized and available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
